		<div id="text-1405623" class="p">
			
		 	
				<a href="http://currawong.net/">Currawong</a> writes <i>"Apple has posted <a href="http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=120150">Security Update 2002-09-20</a> for Mac OS X 10.2 and above in Software Update, fixing a security hole in Terminal.app which could 'allow an attacker to remotely execute arbitrary commands on the user's system.'  Apple also has a <a href="http://www.info.apple.com/usen/security/security_updates.html">useful page listing all the security updates</a> with a short summary and links to what they patch."</i>
		 	
