	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_4302563">It is done via the Software Update application. This app checks in certain intervals (default weekly) if new updates are available and lets the user choose the updates to install. Most updates are also available for download from Apple's website. Apple provides a security mailing list which will alert you to security updates. Since summer, all updates are signed and the signature is being checked by Software Update before installing.</div>
